<Policy>
  <h1>Preservation Policy</h1>
  <p>We archive derivative formats (HTML, EPUB, PDF) and synchronize releases to trusted repositories such as Zenodo for long-term access. Metadata is versioned in Git.</p>
  <p>Checksums accompany all downloads to verify file integrity over time.</p>
</Policy>
